    <div id="service_details_wrapper" class="section_padding_100">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-12">
                    <!-- Service Details Content Area -->
                    <div class="service_details_content">

                        <div class="text-center about_intro">
                            <h3>At Strategic Retirement Partners, we are different.  We focus exclusively on your Retirement Plans, and issues related to them.  We don’t sell money management services or insurance, we focus our time on making your plan better and your life easier.  Whether it is a Defined Benefit or ESOP plan, a Profit Sharing Plan or a 401(K), we are your outsourced experts.</h3>
                        </div>


                        <!-- Service Details Text Area -->
                        <div class="single_part_content mt15">
                            <h4>Fiduciary Protection</h4>
                            <p>Strategic Retirement Partners (SRP) excels in Plan Governance and Fiduciary Education.  DOL and IRS regulations increase each year, so, through a process of managing our proprietary Fiduciary Fitness Program, we work to alleviate and fill any holes in our clients’ fiduciary program.</p>
                        </div>
                        <!-- Service Details Text Area -->
                        <div class="single_part_content">
                            <h4>Vendor Analysis</h4>
                            <p>Many companies have had their record keeper sold and change hands (BMO-OneAmerica, NY Life-John Hancock etc.) in the recent past and may wonder if they are still getting the service and value they had once taken for granted.  SRP excels in Vendor Analysis; since we are product agnostic, we are only interested in making sure that you are receiving the value and service you have come to expect.</p>
                        </div>
                        <!-- Service Details Text Area -->
                        <div class="single_part_content">
                            <h4>Fee Benchmarking</h4>
                            <p>On a regular basis, SRP will utilize our proprietary process of “Live Bid Benchmarking”.  This will help to keep your plan efficient and compliant in the years to come.  Every 3 years we will undertake this process on our clients’ behalf.</p>
                        </div>
                        <!-- Service Details Text Area -->
                        <div class="single_part_content">
                            <h4>Co-Fiduciary Service</h4>
                            <p>Some clients ask only for basic services while others ask for as much help as possible.  We can help customize a service model that works for you and operate as a co-fiduciary on your plan.</p>
                        </div>
                        <!-- Service Details Text Area -->
                        <div class="single_part_content">
                            <h4>Reduce Administrative Burden</h4>
                            <p>With the complexity of ERISA guidelines, it is becoming more and more difficult and time consuming to keep up with all the notification requirements, fund change notices, summary annual reports etc., that must be managed.  We work to remove the non-productive time from your personnel and free them up to focus on issues that directly affect your bottom line.</p>
                        </div>


                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
