                        <h6 class="wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.4s" style="visibility: visible; animation-delay: 0.4s; animation-name: fadeInUp;">Review/Add Liability Driving Investing – Part of the plan assets strategy necessary to track liabilities and minimize the pain of unexpected market shocks.</h6>
                        <h6 class="wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.5s" style="visibility: visible; animation-delay: 0.5s; animation-name: fadeInUp;">Evaluate the Cost of Termination – Determine how long it may take before funding is in place to cover termination costs (funding shortfall).</h6>
